  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA6">
<l>neṟikāṭṭi nīkkutiyō niṉpāṟ karumā</l>
<l>muṟimēṉi kāṭṭutiyō mēṉā ḷaṟiyōmē</l>
<l>yeṉceyvā ṉeṇṇiṉāy kaṇṇaṉē yīturaiyā</l>
<l>yeṉceytā leṉpaṭōm yām.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having shown the path, shall you dispell [us] from your side? Shall you</l>
<l>show [your] black dark sprout body? On a former day we did not know.</l>
<l>What did you count on doing, Kaṇṇaṉ? Say it.</l>
<l>If we do what, what shall we not suffer?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
